Singular
[http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/ever ever][http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/what what]

   1.  No matter which; for any
   2.  What one or ones (of those mentioned or implied). 

'''Example'''

"You can ride everwhat three wheeler you want. Besides, it's goin' to be what it's goin' be."